<div id="banner">
	<h1>Subscribe to this Weblog by Email!</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>I&#8217;ve used <a href="http://www.w3.org/2002/09/rss2email/">my RSS to email aggregator</a> to create an email list for this weblog. If you&#8217;re tired of checking back here every day and would rather receive new stories direct to your email box, then this is for you!</p>

<p>To subscribe, simply send a message to <a href="mailto:aaronswblog-subscribe@notabug.com">aaronswblog-subscribe@notabug.com</a> and reply to the confirmation message you get back.</p>

<p>You can also email for <a href="mailto:aaronswblog-help@notabug.com">help and a description of available commands</a>.</p>

<p><a href="mailto:weblog@aaronsw.com">Let me know</a> what you think of this new service. It&#8217;s trivial for me to set up another one of these, so let me know if you have a favorite site that you&#8217;d like to see turned into an email list.</p>

<p class="posted">posted September 18, 2002 11:53 PM (<a class="category" href="http://www.aaronsw.com/weblog/cat_technology">Technology</a>)  <a href="000606" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

